<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Login Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>New Login Detected</h2>
  <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
  <p>We noticed a new login to your account:</p>

  <table>
    <tr><td><strong>Device:</strong></td><td>{{device}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>IP Address:</strong></td><td>{{ipAddress}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Location:</strong></td><td>{{location}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td><strong>Time:</strong></td><td>{{timestamp}}</td></tr>
  </table>

  <p>If this was you, no action is needed.</p>
  <p><strong>If this wasn't you:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Change your password immediately</li>
    <li>Sign out of all devices</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Best regards,<br/>The Team</p>  
</body>
</html>